sources.description:
A man on his way to closing a million dollar deal has an accident and gets amnesia. She's taking him for a ride...He's giving her the Merry-Go-Round

Director: Aubrey Scotto
Writers: Jack Natteford, Nathanael West 
Stars: Roger Pryor, Wendy Barrie, Claude Gillingwater
Genres: Adventure, Comedy, Romance
